Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinji, did you change\Nthe soup stock?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:45.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, to dried fish flavor.\NIt’s a gift from Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:53.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:59.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re always apologizing!  Do you\Nalways think you’re the one at fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:06.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji, apologies are your conditioned\Nreflex to any kind of confrontation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:06.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:10.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Exactly like that.\NYou’re too self-deprecating!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:14.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now, now, that’s just his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:17.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s so easy to just accept his\Npathetic habits, isn’t it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:20.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But haven’t you been a little\Ntoo easy on Shinji lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:21.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Maybe you and Kaji have\Nhooked up again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:26.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but the fact that you’re happy doesn’t\Nmean that you can just ignore us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:28.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There’s nothing between me and Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:34.69,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Katsuragi, I’ve found a bar\Nthat serves a decent drink.\NHow ‘bout tonight?  Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:40.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve never been around anyone involved\Nin such an indecent relationship before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:43.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re supposed to be our guardian!\NYou hypocrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s disgusting!!
