Dialogue: 4,0:02:46.18,0:02:50.31,Title (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,{\blur0.7}{\pos(320,288)}Death, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:53.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,B-type harmonics test, all green.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Projected adjustment values\Nhave been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:58.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You look tired, Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:00.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, for a lot of private reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.11,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:05.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, how’s the Third Child doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:08.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:12.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I hope that knowing this will\Nboost his confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato!  How were my test scores?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes!  You are Number One!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He beat us easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:31.37,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He beat us so easily it’s pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:34.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He’s great, wonderful, awesome,\Ntoo awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The invincible Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:41.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So that makes our job a\Nlittle easier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:47.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But it also means that we’ll have to do our\Nbest to not be left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:03.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Next stop is Seisho Kabuse.\NNext stop, Seisho Kabuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:06.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Convenient to the Bashar, used books\Nand video game stores...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:10.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Five minutes until evacuation of the\NWestern District is completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:45.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Target is advancing slowly\Nat 2.5 km per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:46.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s going on?\NThe observation center in Fuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...didn’t detect it.  It just suddenly\Nappeared directly above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:55.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Pattern Orange.  No AT Field detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:56.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A new kind of Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The MAGI are withholding judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:04.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn!  A situation like this and\NCommander Ikari’s not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Can you all hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve sent you all of the target’s data.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is all we know right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:26.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Approach it carefully and observe\Nits reactions and, if possible,\Nlure it outside of the city limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:29.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Two of you will back up\Nthe other, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:33.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,All right, ma’am, but I think Shinji\Nought to take point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:41.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, this is a job for the highest rated,\Nbravest, Number One synchro-ratio\Nholder, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Or don’t you feel up to it, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:48.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll show you how it ought\Nto be done, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:51.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Wh...what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, you two cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:56.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Isn’t that what you said, Misato?\N“You are Number One!”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,And combat is a man’s job, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Talk about out of date!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.49,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 02 will back him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 00 will back him up as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t believe those kids are doing\Nthis without my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:11.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji’s getting more manly, isn’t he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:13.90,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, I’m going to have to chew him\Nout when he gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:16.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You might just be a good teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:35.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ayanami, Asuka, are you in position yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:36.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:39.70,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You know an Eva can’t move that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}I’ll have to stop it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:09.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:12.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Pattern Blue!!  Angel confirmed!\NDirectly beneath Unit 01!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A... a shadow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?!  I can’t believe it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:23.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji, get out of there!  Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.37,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:26.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You idiot!  What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:31.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato, what’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:34.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato?  Asuka!  Ayanami!  Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato?!  Can you hear me, Misato?!\NMisato!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Eject the plug!  Send the signal!\N{\c&H00E3FE&}Misato?!  Can you hear me, Misato?!\NMisato!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:39.49,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No response!  It’s not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato!  Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:47.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka!  Rei!  Rescue Unit 01!  Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:50.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That idiot.  He can get an A on a test\Nbut not in the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It disappeared again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The city is sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.67,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka!  Rei!  Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:23.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,B...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:24.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Wait!\N{\c&H00E3FE&}B...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:26.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 01 and Ikari are still in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:30.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is an order.  Retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Major Katsuragi must feel awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:48.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,They reeled the umbilical cable back in,\Nbut the other end was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Without power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:52.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There’s not much energy\Nin the internal batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If Shinji doesn’t waste it groping\Nblindly in the dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...if he stays in the most minimal\Nlife-support mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...then he can survive for 16 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:03.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Second Tank Battalion deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.37,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger.  Hold your current\Npositions and stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:08.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sub laser circuit has been opened.\NTransmitting data now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:09.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Confirmed.  New line transmitting data.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The UN forces have completely\Nsurrounded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shadow status?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:18.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It hasn’t moved.  It stopped\Nspreading once it reached a diameter\Njust over 600 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,By the way, is there a use for\Nthose ground troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:25.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,They’re supposed to allow us\Nto apply pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:26.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:31.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Taking matters into his own hands,\Ndefying Operations.  He got what\Nhe was asking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:36.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Just because he got a little better score\Nthan mine, he had to go and show me\Nhow it ought to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:38.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What a dummkopf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:44.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?  Are my comments about\NShinji pissing you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do you pilot Eva just for\Nthe praise of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:53.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  I don’t need anybody’s\Napproval but my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:55.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Cut it out, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.90,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, he acted arbitrarily and\Nwithout consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:03.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So...  I’ll just have to punish him\Nwhen he comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:26.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I never thought sleeping could\Nbe this exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:33.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Still nothing but white noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:38.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No radar or sonar reflections at all.\NThis space must be too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:42.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s been 12 hours since I switched\Nto life-support mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,My life will end in four or five hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:51.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, that shadow is actually\Nthe Angel’s body?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:59.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Correct.  It’s 680 meters in diameter with\Na thickness of three nanometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sustained within that ultra-thin space\Nis an inverted AT Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Inside that field is a region of space\Nthat can only be defined by abstract\Nmathematics, a Sea of Dirac.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:09.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It could be connected\Nto another universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What about the sphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:14.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It disappears when the imaginary\Ncircuit of the body closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:17.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The object in the sky is only a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:21.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So the black shadow that swallowed\NUnit 01 is the real target.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then there’s no way that we can fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:32.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The water is getting cloudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The purification system is breaking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It smells in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Blood!  This place smells like blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.90,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  I hate this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:44.30,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why can’t I open this lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.67,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Open up!  Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.37,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato, tell me what’s going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato!  Asuka!  Ayanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Dr. Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Please...  someone help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.62,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A forced Eva salvage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:06.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s the only possibility that might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:12.06,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We would drop all 992 existing\NN2 mines into its center...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...while simultaneously activating the\NAT Fields of both remaining Evas...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:19.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...in such a way as to disrupt the\Nhypothetical circuit that encloses the\NAngel’s pocket interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:22.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If we concentrate enough explosive\Npower into the same microsecond...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:25.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...we might destroy the Angel along with\Nthe Dirac Sea that makes up its body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:29.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But the damage to the Eva would be...\NShinji wouldn’t...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What kind of rescue operation is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:34.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This operation’s priority is to\Nrecover the Eva itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.62,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That the body may be severely damaged\Nor destroyed in the process\Nhas no bearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:40.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The pilot’s life is not our concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:50.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If Shinji’s lost, it’s your fault!\NJust remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:55.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why are you and Commander Ikari\Nso worried about Unit 01?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What in the hell is an Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:01.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve given you all the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:02.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:07.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:14.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m taking command of\Nthis entire operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:23.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Forward all flights to Kansai International\NAirport.  Contact Air Traffic Control and\Nthe air transport divisions of the JADF.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:28.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In,{\fad(170,0)}The Second Impact,\Nthe Instrumentality Project, Adam...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade Out,{\fad(0,170)}There are so many secrets that\NI’m in the dark about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:45.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.62,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.16,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:54.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I am you.\NThis self incorporates another self.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The self has always been composed\Nof two selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, the self which is observed and the\Nself which observes itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:09.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,To expound, the Shinji Ikari that exists in\Nyour mind is only one Shinji Ikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:12.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...there’s also the Shinji Ikari in\NMisato Katsuragi’s mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:13.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...the Shinji Ikari in\NAsuka Soryu’s mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...the Shinji Ikari in Rei Ayanami’s mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.45,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and the Shinji Ikari in\NGendo Ikari’s mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:19.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,All are different Shinji Ikaris...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:22.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but each of them is a true Shinji Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:25.49,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What you fear are the Shinji Ikaris who\Nexist in the minds of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m just afraid of being hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:30.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re afraid of being hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who is bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Father is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The father who deserted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.01,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, I’m the one who’s bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:43.11,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re always apologizing!  Do you\Nalways think you’re the one at fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, you just believe that\Nyou’re worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:51.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t you trust your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:54.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I thought I hated my father,\Nbut now I’m not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:57.16,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good work, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:01.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,My father called me by my name.\NI was praised by my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:06.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Will you spend your life regurgitating\Nand re-digesting those few\Npleasant memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:09.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If I trust their words,\Nit’s enough to keep me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:11.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Even though you know you’re\Ndeceiving yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:14.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Everybody does it!\NThat’s how everyone survives!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:19.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If you will not believe that you can change\Nyourself, you will be unable to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:23.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This world is filled with too much pain\Nand suffering to keep going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,For example, you can’t swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:26.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Humans aren’t made to float.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That is self-deception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t care what you want to call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:34.70,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You have been shutting your eyes and\Nears to that which you wished to avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:37.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,His sister was injured during the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:38.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who cares what the others say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:43.01,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  I don’t want to hear this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,See?  You’re running from reality again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:51.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No one can justify their existence\Nby linking their happiest moments into\Na kind of rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,In particular, I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:59.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve found something I can do to feel\Ngood.  Something I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:07.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,In theory, the entry plug’s energy reserves\Nshould be reaching their expiration point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:10.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The plug suit’s life support system will\Nbe getting close to redline.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:13.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Advance the schedule by 12 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:16.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let’s do it while there’s a possibility\Nthat Shinji’s still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Father, am I unwanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:38.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It was really yourself that\Nyou ran away from.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:44.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s right!  He may be guilty\Nof killing his own wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He killed his own wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  Mother was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji, you must not run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:58.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I hate this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:04.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I hate this loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:13.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The heating and the oxygen circulation\Nare already out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:23.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s useless, the suit is giving out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:26.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...tired of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:32.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:07.62,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:16.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is this enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:22.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, that’s good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Evas are in position and standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:29.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,AT Fields are ready to generate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,T-minus 60 seconds to mine drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:44.39,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Status report!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.45,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:48.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,All meters and gauges are\Ngoing off the scale!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But we haven’t done anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No way!  Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:54.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 01’s power level has to be at zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:28.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I...  am I piloting a thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:34.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,My God, what kind of monster\Nhave we copied from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:38.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In,{\fad(170,0)}I know that the Evas aren’t just\Ncopies of the First Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:44.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade Out,{\fad(0,170)}But what is NERV going to do with them\Nonce all the Angels have been destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:23.39,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji?!  Shinji?!  Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:27.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji?!  Are you all right, Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:38.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Didn’t you say you were going\Nto punish him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:51.45,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve never seen the Eva looking as\Nhorrible as it did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:54.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are the Evas really on our side?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:58.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,They may hate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:02.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I think Major Katsuragi\Nnoticed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I see.  Let her be for now.
